      "ja": "んぎぃぃっ！♥　気持ち良いの止まらにゃいぃぃ♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "211.2",
      "line_index": 211,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c92e48c5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おまんこ気持ちいぃぃっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "213.0",
      "line_index": 213,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "27b506f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぐちゅぐちゅと卑猥な音を響かせ、指の出し入れを繰り返すヴォイド。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "214.0",
      "line_index": 214,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2036908c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "本能の赴くままに快感を求め、快感に甘い悲鳴を上げ続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "217.0",
      "line_index": 217,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "47d9c89f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふぅっ！♥　んおおおっ！♥　ほっ！♥　んお……おおおおっ！！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "217.2",
      "line_index": 217,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "47d9c89f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おまんこ壊れちゃうぅ♥　マスターっ！♥　マスターっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "219.2",
      "line_index": 219,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "81d0816e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思考が支配されてしまったヴォイド。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "220.2",
      "line_index": 220,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a96d077e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そうされることに喜びを感じてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.0",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d6de4309",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マスターっ♥　もっと、もっとぉ……！♥　んほぉぉ！！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.2",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d6de4309",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もっと滅茶苦茶に……んんっ！♥　んあ！♥　あっ！♥　ああぁっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "226.0",
      "line_index": 226,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "414cb853",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マスターになら何をされれてもいいっ♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "226.2",
      "line_index": 226,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "414cb853",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もっとわたしを犯してっ！♥　マスターっ！♥　マスターっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "226.4",
      "line_index": 226,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "414cb853",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "好きっ！♥　好き好き好き好きぃぃぃっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "229.0",
      "line_index": 229,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9c26b39e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もうマスターへの想いを抑えきれないっ！♥　マスターが欲しいっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "229.2",
      "line_index": 229,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9c26b39e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マスターのおちんちんが欲しいっ！♥　マスターの子種が欲しいっ！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "232.0",
      "line_index": 232,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7112eaf1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マスターに孕まされたいっ！♥　マスターと添い遂げたいぃぃぃっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "234.2",
      "line_index": 234,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "673bb05",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ひたすらにあそこを掻き回し続けるヴォイド。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.0",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "46eceb3c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああああぁっ！♥　また波がクるっ！♥　すごいのクるっ！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.2",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "46eceb3c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "マスター！♥　わたしの絶頂するところ見て！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.4",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "46eceb3c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いやらしいわたしを見てっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "244.0",
      "line_index": 244,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "49004f34",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あああっ！♥　マスターっ！♥　マスター！♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "244.2",
      "line_index": 244,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "49004f34",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "クるっ！♥　クりゅぅぅぅっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "273.0",
      "line_index": 273,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5885de12",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふおおおっ！♥　んお、おっ！♥　ふおおおおおおっ！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "275.0",
      "line_index": 275,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5b54e6bb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "大きくのけ反らせながら絶頂に達するヴォイド。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "276.0",
      "line_index": 276,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "37419d3f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "真っ白な愛液が指の隙間からごぷりと溢れ、大量の潮が尿道から噴き出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "279.0",
      "line_index": 279,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2d883253",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う、あっ！♥　うう、出て、りゅぅ……♥　これ、ぎもぢ……いぃ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "281.0",
      "line_index": 281,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c8998e4b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何度も絶頂の波に襲われ、ぷしゃぷしゃと勢いよく潮を噴かせるヴォイド。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "282.0",
      "line_index": 282,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8eb5c9ce",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらに快感を欲する本能は、絶頂しているあそこを掻き回し、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "282.2",
      "line_index": 282,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8eb5c9ce",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ヴォイドをさらに絶頂へと誘い続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "285.0",
      "line_index": 285,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cf18bb26",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う、あ……！♥　気持ち、いいの……と、止まらないぃ……！！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "288.0",
      "line_index": 288,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "91a3063a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あっ……！♥　ぁあ……んあ……！♥　あ、あぁ……ぁぁ……っ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "290.0",
      "line_index": 290,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cba61469",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ヴォイドは快感に耐えきれず、絶頂しながら気を失ってしまった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "291.0",
      "line_index": 291,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c6a99ffd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも身体は絶頂し続け、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "291.2",
      "line_index": 291,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c6a99ffd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "気絶しながらも何度も潮を噴かせ続けているのであった。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
